abstract: >
  AI Visibility is a free, open-source WordPress plugin that gives site
  owners technical control over how AI platforms (ChatGPT, Gemini, Perplexity,
  Claude, and others) crawl and represent their site. It generates an llms.txt
  file, manages robots.txt rules for 30+ AI bot user-agents, injects
  Schema.org structured data as JSON-LD, and adds HTML meta tags for AI crawl
  control. No external API calls, no visitor data collection.
